    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Sets of vessels intended for use on a washstand generally including a basin and ewer, but may also include a soap dish and chamber pot.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
